# Croncat journalism workflow dossiers
# Per-story JSON records (dossier + brief + post record) produced by the
# journalism pipeline. Kept local by default — Phase 4 turns this directory
# into a public transparency archive, at which point this rule will be
# removed selectively.
dossiers/

# Croncat journalism workflow drafts
# Dry-run draft posts land here as <story_id>_<post_type>.md. Local-only;
# the directory itself is tracked via a .gitkeep sentinel.
drafts/*
!drafts/.gitkeep
